TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);
$power = $a + 1;
$coeff = 1 / $power;
$funct = "(ln(x)^$power)/$power ";

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Evaluate the indefinite integral.
$BR \[ \int \frac{(\ln(x))^$a}{x} dx \]
$BR $BR Integral = \{ans_rule( 30) \}
$BR
EOT

